# PHPStan Static Analysis

## When to use

- Running PHPStan or Larastan static analysis on a project
- Configuring PHPStan levels (0-9) and rules
- Generating or updating a PHPStan baseline
- Fixing PHPStan reported errors (type mismatches, undefined methods, etc.)
- Setting up custom PHPStan extensions or ignoring errors

## Keywords

`phpstan`, `larastan`, `static analysis`, `phpstan level`, `phpstan baseline`, `type safety`, `phpstan analyse`, `phpstan neon`
